[[File:Spiritual mage icon.png|left]]
The '''Spiritual mage''' is a potent [[Magic]] [[Slayer monsters|Slayer monster]] found in the [[God Wars Dungeon]] that can easily kill low-level players. [[Protect from Magic]] and high prayer bonus is highly recommended for anyone wanting to 'camp' these monsters. Like all monsters in the [[God Wars Dungeon]], they are aggressive to any players that do not wear items showing loyalty to their god. Spiritual mages require 83 [[Slayer]] to kill. Completion of [[Death Plateau]] is required before Spiritual creatures can be assigned as a [[Slayer task]]{{CiteTwitter|author=Mod Ash|url=https://twitter.com/JagexAsh/status/920581364457582592|date=18 October 2017|archiveurl=https://archive.is/LyNmY|archivedate=27 May 2020|quote=[can Spiritual Creatures be assigned as a task if Death Plateau hasn't been done?] No, they can't.}}. Just like [[Spiritual ranger]]s and [[Spiritual warrior]]s, which require 63 and 68 Slayer respectively, there are spiritual mages for each god.

Slaying a Spiritual mage in the God Wars Dungeon is a requirement for the [[Elite Fremennik Diary]] and slaying a Spiritual mage in the Wilderness God Wars Dungeon is a requirement for the [[Elite Wilderness Diary]].

Spiritual mages mostly drop runes and pure essence. They are also known for their [[dragon boots]] drop.

